---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: '2026 Budget Tax Impact: Equipment Purchase Planning',
  slug: '2026-budget-tax-impact',
  excerpt: 'How the 2026 budget affects equipment purchase tax benefits. Plan your buying strategy with 0% down payment financing.',
  date: '2026-01-22',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Tax Planning',
  image: '/images/blog/tax-planning.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['budget 2026', 'tax impact', 'equipment financing', '0% down payment'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Tax Planning</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Budget 2026 Overview</h2>

      <p>The annual budget announces tax policies. 2026 budget affects equipment purchases. Know the changes. Plan accordingly. Save money.</p>

      <h2>Key Budget 2026 Measures</h2>

      <h3>Capital Allowance</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Maintained at current rates</li>
        <li><strong>Initial allowance:</strong> 20-40% continues</li>
        <li><strong>Annual allowance:</strong> 10-20% continues</li>
        <li><strong>Impact:</strong> No negative changes</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Special Incentives</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Investment tax allowance:</strong> May expand coverage</li>
        <li><strong>Green technology:</strong> Enhanced incentives</li>
        <li><strong>Automation equipment:</strong> Additional support</li>
        <li><strong>Check details:</strong> For qualifying equipment</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Budget Impact on Financing</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #D4A574; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">Area</th>
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">Budget 2026 Impact</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Down Payment Rules</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">No change - Banks still require 10-20%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F5F0E8;">
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Equipment Age</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Banks still limit to 5 years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Interest Deduction</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #E8F5E9;">Still 100% deductible</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Ing Heng Credit: Unaffected Advantages</h2>

      <p>Our benefits continue regardless of budget:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>0% down payment:</strong> Always available</li>
        <li><strong>100% full loan:</strong> Complete financing</li>
        <li><strong>NO age limit:</strong> Any equipment</li>
        <li><strong>Fast approval:</strong> 24-48 hours</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>New Budget Opportunities</h2>

      <h3>Green Equipment Incentives</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Electric vehicles:</strong> Potential tax credits</li>
        <li><strong>Energy-efficient machines:</strong> Enhanced deductions</li>
        <li><strong>Solar equipment:</strong> Special allowances</li>
        <li><strong>Apply early:</strong> For new incentives</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Industry-Specific Support</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Manufacturing:</strong> Automation incentives</li>
        <li><strong>Construction:</strong> Equipment support</li>
        <li><strong>Logistics:</strong> Modernization allowances</li>
        <li><strong>Check eligibility:</strong> For your industry</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Post-Budget Planning Strategy</h2>

      <h3>Step 1: Review Budget Announcements</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Read Budget 2026 summary</li>
        <li>Identify relevant changes</li>
