      <ul>
        <li>Target qualifying equipment</li>
        <li>Time purchases for optimal benefits</li>
        <li>Use 0% down payment for cash flow</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>0% Down Payment Advantage</h2>

      <p>With budget changes, 0% down payment helps:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Preserve cash:</strong> During uncertain times</li>
        <li><strong>Quick action:</strong> Respond to new incentives</li>
        <li><strong>Flexible timing:</strong> Buy when beneficial</li>
        <li><strong>Same deductions:</strong> As other financing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Used Equipment After Budget</h2>

      <p>Used equipment remains attractive:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Same allowances:</strong> On lower cost</li>
        <li><strong>Banks restrict:</strong> Still 5-year limit</li>
        <li><strong>Ing Heng accepts:</strong> Any age equipment</li>
        <li><strong>Cost advantage:</strong> More equipment for same budget</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2026 Budget Action Plan</h2>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>Study Budget 2026:</strong> When released</li>
        <li><strong>Consult accountant:</strong> Understand impact</li>
        <li><strong>Identify opportunities:</strong> New incentives</li>
        <li><strong>Plan purchases:</strong> Around benefits</li>
        <li><strong>Use 0% down:</strong> Preserve cash</li>
        <li><strong>Act quickly:</strong> On limited-time offers</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Real Budget Planning</h2>

      <p>"Budget 2025 announced new green incentives. Accountant explained the benefits. Changed equipment purchase plans. Bought electric forklift instead of diesel. Got special allowance. Saved extra RM8,000 in taxes. 0% down payment preserved cash. Always check budget announcements. New incentives can save thousands. Plan purchases around budget measures."</p>

      <p><em>— Karen Lee, Logistics Manager</em></p>

      <h2>Maximize Budget 2026 Benefits</h2>

      <p>Budget changes bring opportunities. 0% down payment maximizes flexibility. 100% full loan expands options. NO age limit increases choices.</p>

      <p>We approve in 24-48 hours. Plan your 2026 equipment purchases around budget benefits today.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Maximize Budget Benefits</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Get 0% down payment equipment financing and maximize Budget 2026 incentives.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Equipment Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  ol li {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  ol li::before {
    content: none;
  }

  br {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
